data.description: Don't miss this completely updated Jamestown township  4-bedroom 3 full bathroom home with outbuilding and updated mechanicals under $450,000!  (Furnace, AC & water heater replaced in 2023) This home is a showstopper with all its high-end new finishes and plenty of space and separation to accommodate every style of living!  This home features an open floor plan with cathedral ceilings with a stunning brand-new kitchen.  Striking 42' upper cabinetry with herringbone backsplash tile, built in hood, quartz counter tops, custom hardware, and new Navy appliances (can be controlled via Wi-Fi).  The living room has a modern electric fireplace with custom-built in shelving around the fireplace and ceiling fan.  Upstairs you will find 2 bedrooms including the primary, which will immediately hav you falling in love!  Soaring cathedral ceilings, and large picture windows plus a large closet and plenty of space for your furniture make this room hard to beat.  The additional bedroom and completely remodeled bathroom with quartz countertops and walk in tile shower which is sure to impress.  Wander downstairs to an additional family room with custom built coffered ceilings with wood accents, a large closet for storage plus an additional bedroom/office and another fully updated bathroom.  The lowest level has another suite with a large bedroom and walk in closet plus an attached bathroom.  The lower bathroom includes tile shower, new vanity with solid surface tops. Thinking you need room for storage?  Well don't miss the 15x24 ft out building with concrete floor and a 10x12 door plus a full concrete pad for easy access.  This home is a dream.  Pride of ownership is easily seen throughout.  You don't want to miss this house!
